WESTERN SOUTH ATLANTIC.
URUGUAY.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY IN PROGRESS UNTIL 17 FEB BY
   M/V RAMFORM VANGUARD TOWING 12 7000 METER LONG
   CABLES ALONG TRACKLINES BETWEEN:
   A. 35-25.15S 051-30.15W AND 34-46.28S 052-30.72W.
   B. 34-50.78S 052-35.23W AND 35-29.80S 051-34.78W.

2. CANCEL THIS MSG 18 FEB 13.
